metadata.name: Waves for 4CI "Shin in hyo byo" Op.1-1 by AI
metadata.description: This is a series of new AI re-creations of mera's past works on SuperRare. AI is learning the images, titles, and descriptions of mera's works. In the future, artists may disappear as AI evolves, but I hope to enjoy the chaos of our time. Take a look at some of the new "my" artworks.
